text.tspan: - Five circles because of five letters in 'EHRET'
- First circle: stroke width 10 px, approximately the stroke width
of the 'H' Lato letter with font-style bold and font-size 72px
- Circles: stroke width 7 px, approximately the stroke width
of the 'H' Lato letter with font-style normal and font-size 72px
so that the distance between them on the
right is a multiple of 0.618: ai = ai+1 * 0.618, i = 1, 2, 3 ...
one pixel difference between tops at the right
gray shades from white to black by delta of 25%
